RUNELF_NOWAIT(1)

NAME
    runelf_nowait - run an ELF program without waiting

SYNOPSIS
    runelf_nowait path [arg ...]

DESCRIPTION
    runelf_nowait is a shell built-in that executes an ext2 ELF program and
    immediately returns to the shell.

    Unlike runelf_bg, the process is not tracked as a reattachable shell job.

SEE ALSO
    runelf(1), runelf_bg(1), shell(1)
